    "body": "I have commented out that line on a locally compiled version, and can confirm the beacon node uses GOMAXPROCS set from the environment. The reason I brought this up is because my machine has 24 cores running various docker containers. Without setting GOMAXPROCS I have observed all 24-cores go up 100% in CPU for a prolonged time (note CPU does come down before going up again). Setting GOMAXPROCS to 2 is enough for a performant and reliable prysm instance.\r\n\r\nNote that line 186 in cmd/validator/main.go also has the same setting.",
